# ── Contact form ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional. If unset, the contact form gracefully opens the visitor's mail client
# (mailto:) instead of POSTing anywhere — so the site works with zero config.
#
# To enable real form delivery:
#   1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io (or any endpoint accepting JSON).
#   2. Copy the endpoint URL below.
#   3. Re-deploy. The form will POST { name, email, message } as JSON.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ is required so the value is available in the browser.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
